20caf%C3%A9's%20WiFi.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20had%20cut%20my%20internet%20off%20because%20I%20couldn't%20even%20pay%20for%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEvery%20morning%2C%20he'd%20put%20on%20a%20suit%2C%20pack%20his%20laptop%2C%20and%20set%20up%20shop%20at%20Panera.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20would%20think%20I%20was%20in%20there%20handling%20business%2C%20but%20I%20was%20actually%20looking%20for%20a%20job%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey%20used%20to%20come%20around%20with%20these%20free%20samples%20every%20day%2C%20and%20you%20could%20get%20as%20many%20as%20you%20wanted%2C%20so%20those%20free%20samples%20were%20my%20meal%20for%20the%20day.%20It%20was%20one%20of%20the%20most%20humbling%20experiences%20of%20my%20life.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBrown%20knew%20what%20it%20was%20like%20to%20live%20without%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERaised%20by%20a%20single%20mother%20in%20Detroit%2C%20and%20it%20wasn't%20until%20he%20went%20to%20a%20friend's%20house%20that%20he%20realized%20it%20wasn't%20the%20norm%20to%20sleep%20without%20a%20bed.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20thought%20beds%20were%20for%20grown-ups%20because%20you%20need%20a%20good%20night's%20rest%20to%20go%20to%20work%20the%20next%20day.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20just%20became%20very%20curious%20about%20money%20at%20a%20super%20young%20age%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228e3108d3-b64a-43b2-8ee2-866dd55b6d48%5C%22%3EBuilding%20a%20six-figure%20portfolio%20in%20college%2C%20and%20then%20losing%20it%20all%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20reading%20books%20like%20%26quot%3BThink%20and%20Grow%20Rich%2C%26quot%3B%20Brown%20figured%20that%20investing%20was%20his%20ticket%20to%20wealth%2C%20so%20he%20took%20the%20%242%2C000%20he%20received%20as%20high%20school%20graduation%20money%20to%20the%20bank%20to%20invest.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20teller%20asked%20him%20two%20questions%3A%20%26quot%3B'Why%20do%20you%20want%20to%20invest%3F'%20I'm%20like%2C%20'To%20be%20rich.'%20I%20thought%20it%20was%20a%20silly%20question.%20And%20then%20she%20said%2C%20'So%20you%20want%20aggressive%20funds%2C%20right%3F'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETwo%20years%20later%2C%20he%20returned%20to%20the%20bank%20eager%20to%20check%20in%20on%20his%20investments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20down%20to%20%24700%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BMy%20heart%20just%20dropped.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBrown%20withdrew%20the%20remaining%20funds%2C%20figuring%20he'd%20rather%20lose%20the%20money%20himself%20so%20he%20could%20at%20least%20understand%20%3Cem%3Ehow%3C%2Fem%3E%20he%20lost%20it%20than%20leave%20it%20up%20to%20the%20bank.%20He%20spent%20%24200%20on%20a%20pair%20of%20Jordans%20%E2%80%94%20%26quot%3BI%20didn't%20want%20to%20see%20the%20whole%20money%20just%20disappear%20and%20I%20had%20nothing%20to%20show%20for%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20%E2%80%94%20and%20began%20his%20investing%20career%20as%20a%20college%20freshman%20with%20%24500.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22545%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22jason%20brown%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F688269ca3d5881a51c1df009%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22409%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBrown%20worked%20for%20Sprint%20PCS%20on%20the%20weekends.%20His%20initial%20goal%20was%20to%20make%20enough%20money%20from%20the%20stock%20market%20to%20afford%20to%20take%20one%20Saturday%20off.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Jason%20Brown%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBuying%20Sprint%20stock%20was%20a%20natural%20place%20for%20him%20to%20start.%20He%20worked%20for%20the%20company%20on%20the%20weekends%2C%20earning%20%248%20an%20hour%20selling%20cellphones.%20If%20he%20could%20make%20%2450%20in%20the%20stock%20market%2C%20he%20could%20afford%20to%20take%20one%20Saturday%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20plan%20was%20simple%3A%20%26quot%3BOur%20stock%20was%20%245%20at%20Sprint%2C%20and%20I%20had%20%24500.%20I%20could%20buy%20100%20shares%2C%20and%20all%20I%20needed%20it%20to%20do%20was%20move%20%240.50.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20bought%20100%20shares%20at%20%245%2C%20watched%20in%20dismay%20as%20the%20stock%20gradually%20fell%20to%20%244%2C%20and%20then%20regained%20optimism%20as%20it%20climbed%20back%20to%20%245.%20As%20the%20price%20fluctuated%2C%20he%20formulated%20a%20new%20plan%3A%20Get%20out%20at%20%245%20to%20break%20even%2C%20wait%20for%20the%20stock%20to%20fall%20to%20%244%2C%20and%20then%20get%20back%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20got%20in%20at%20four%2C%20it%20went%20back%20up%20to%20five%2C%20and%20I%20made%20my%20first%20hundred%20dollars%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20what%20really%20changed%20my%20life.%20I%20was%20like%2C%20'Woah.%20It%20worked.'%20And%20not%20only%20did%20I%20make%20%2450%2C%20I%20made%20%24100%2C%20so%20that's%20two%20Saturdays%20I%20can%20take%20off.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20later%20learned%20that%20he'd%20stumbled%20into%20a%20strategy%20known%20as%20channeling.%20From%20there%2C%20he%20spent%20all%20his%20free%20time%20reading%20stock%20charts%20and%20patterns.%20He%20grew%20his%20account%20to%20six%20figures%2C%20dropped%20out%20of%20college%2C%20moved%20to%20the%20suburbs%2C%20and%20bought%20a%20Lexus%20GS300.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221125%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22jason%20brown%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68826da2f748d8c055f63842%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22845%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBrown%20dropped%20out%20of%20college%20to%20trade%20full-time.%20He%20eventually%20returned%20to%20Wayne%20State%20University%20and%20got%20his%20degree%20in%20finance.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Jason%20Brown%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBrown%20had%20his%20eyes%20on%20a%20%24500%2C000%20condo%20he%20wanted%20to%20buy%20in%20cash%2C%20and%20he%20was%20confident%20he%20could%20make%20the%20money%20in%20one%20trade.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20up%20%24100%2C000%20in%20my%20trade%2C%20but%20because%20I%20was%20not%20up%20%24500%2C000%2C%20I%20was%20like%2C%20that's%20not%20enough.%20That%20trade%20ended%20up%20reversing%20on%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20just%20became%20this%20whole%20scenario%20of%20gambling%2C%20hoping%2C%20praying%20it%20goes%20back%20up.%20I%20had%20no%20emotional%20control.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUltimately%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20just%20blew%20up%20the%20account.%20I'm%20flat%20broke.%20I%20move%20back%20home.%20I%20have%20to%20sell%20my%20car.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22121e52b9-85e0-4dce-9a6c-ef1171b57a09%5C%22%3EUsing%20principle-based%20investing%20to%20build%20a%20seven-figure%20portfolio%20from%20scratch%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBrown%20was%20determined%20to%20get%20back%20into%20the%20stock%20market%2C%20but%20knew%20he'd%20have%20to%20do%20things%20differently.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20took%20a%20job%20selling%20cellphones%20again%2C%20this%20time%20at%20Verizon.%20He%20lived%20off%20his%20hourly%20pay%20and%20used%20his%20commissions%20to%20trade.%20He%20also%20started%20hosting%20local%20seminars%20from%20coffee%20shops%20and%20libraries%2C%20teaching%20community%20members%20what%20he'd%20learned%20from%20losing%20so%20much%20money%2C%20and%20he%20started%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2F%40brownreport%2Ffeatured%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20YouTube%20channel%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20document%20his%20experience%20trading%20options.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20started%20following%20a%20few%20key%20principles%20to%20ensure%20he%20would%20never%20have%20to%20rely%20on%20Panera%20samples%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20You%20never%20go%20broke%20taking%20a%20profit.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EBrown%20could%20have%20profited%20%24100%2C000%20from%20the%20trade%20that%20ultimately%20wiped%20out%20his%20account%2C%20but%20%26quot%3BI%20thought%20I%20had%20to%20make%20it%20all%20in%20one%20trade.%20I%20needed%20one%20trade%20to%20make%20me%20half%20a%20million%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20The%20experience%20taught%20him%20that%2C%20rather%20than%20succumb%20to%20greed%2C%20%26quot%3Btake%20the%20money%20and%20find%20another%20trade.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20Know%20your%20'I'm%20wrong%20level.'%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EIn%20his%20early%2020s%2C%20Brown%20never%20considered%20his%20%26quot%3BI'm%20wrong%20level%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20explained.%20%26quot%3BI%20only%20thought%2C%20'What%20would%20happen%20if%20this%20goes%20right%3F%20I'm%20getting%20a%20condo.'%20I%20never%20stopped%20to%20think%2C%20'If%20I'm%20wrong%2C%20I'll%20lose%20it%20all%20and%20I%20have%20to%20move%20back%20home.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20he%20knows%20exactly%20when%20he%20needs%20to%20cut%20his%20losses%20and%20shut%20down%20a%20trade.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22541%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22jason%20brown%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68827f7a3d5881a51c1df28e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22785%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBrown%20and%20his%20family%20reside%20in%20Detroit.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Jason%20Brown%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20Follow%20the%201%3A3%20risk-reward%20ratio.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%26quot%3BAny%20trade%20I%20take%20has%20to%20have%20a%20one-to-three%20risk-reward%20ratio%2C%20where%20I%20risk%20one%20dollar%20to%20make%20three%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BBecause%20I've%20found%20that%20you%20could%20be%20wrong%20two%20times%20and%20be%20right%20on%20the%20third%20time%2C%20and%20you%20would%20be%20back%20at%20break%20even.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20say%20he%20has%20%243%20to%20work%20with.%20If%20he%20risks%20%241%20to%20make%20%243%2C%20if%20he%20loses%20one%2C%20he's%20down%20to%20%242%3B%20if%20he%20loses%20again%2C%20he's%20down%20to%20%241%3B%20if%20he's%20right%20the%20third%20time%20and%20it%20makes%20him%20%243%2C%20he's%20back%20up%20to%20%244.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%2C%20I%20can%20still%20be%20profitable%20and%20be%20wrong%20two%20out%20of%20three%20times%2C%20as%20long%20as%20I've%20got%20that%20discipline%20to%20only%20risk%20one%20dollar%20trying%20to%20make%20three%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E4.%20The%20stock%20market%20doesn't%20care%20that%20rent%20is%20due%20next%20week.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Trading%20has%20never%20worked%20well%20for%20Brown%20when%20he's%20had%20to%20put%20pressure%20on%20his%20investments%20to%20make%20a%20certain%20amount%20within%20a%20specific%20timeframe%20to%20cover%20rent%20or%20a%20car%20payment%2C%20for%20example.%20That%20pressure%20%26quot%3Bwill%20have%20you%20doing%20things%20you%20wouldn't%20normally%20do%20because%20you%20fear%20missing%20a%20payment%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20started%20seeing%20a%20lot%20of%20success%20once%20he%20had%20zero%20debt%2C%20at%20least%20six%20months'%20worth%20of%20living%20expenses%20set%20aside%2C%20and%20was%20living%20well%20within%20his%20means.%20The%20lack%20of%20pressure%20allowed%20him%20to%20keep%20his%20emotions%20out%20of%20his%20trades.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFollowing%20these%20four%20principles%20helped%20Brown%20grow%20his%20account%20back%20to%20six%20figures%20in%20about%20a%20year%20and%20a%20half.%20And%2C%20about%20five%20years%20after%20starting%20from%20scratch%2C%20one%20big%20trade%20sent%20him%20into%20the%20seven-figure%20club.%20He%20used%20a%20chunk%20of%20those%20earnings%20to%20pay%20off%20his%20mortgage%20completely.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20lowered%20my%20expenses%2C%20so%20I%20don't%20need%20as%20much%20from%20the%20stock%20market%2C%20which%20allows%20me%20to%20keep%20my%20emotions%20in%20control%20and%20not%20force%20the%20stock%20market%20to%20do%20something%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Brown.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBI%20confirmed%20his%20current%20seven-figure%20net%20worth%20by%20reviewing%20an%20account%20summary%20that%20shows%20his%202024%20investment%20activity.%3C%