ms.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle%20DeepMind's%20CEO%20says%20there%20is%20a%20simple%20reason%20Meta%20is%20spending%20millions%20of%20dollars%20to%20attract%20AI%20talent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMeta%20right%20now%20are%20not%20at%20the%20frontier%2C%20maybe%20they'll%20they'll%20manage%20to%20get%20back%20on%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Demis%20Hassabis%20on%20an%20episode%20of%20the%20%26quot%3BLex%20Fridman%26quot%3B%20podcast%20published%20on%20Thursday.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20probably%20rational%20what%20they're%20doing%20from%20their%20perspective%20because%20they're%20behind%20and%20they%20need%20to%20do%20something.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20last%20few%20weeks%2C%20Meta%20launched%20an%20all-out%20talent%20war%2C%20offering%20researchers%20from%20frontier%20labs%20such%20as%20OpenAI%20up%20to%20%24100%20million%20pay%20packages%20to%20join%20its%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-ceo-mark-zuckerberg-announces-superintelligence-ai-division-internal-memo-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Esuperintelligence%20division%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Recent%20big-name%20hires%20include%20former%20GitHub%20chief%20Nat%20Friedman%2C%20Scale%20AI's%20former%20CEO%20Alexandr%20Wang%2C%20and%20former%20OpenAI%20researchers%20Shengjia%20Zhao%2C%20Shuchao%20Bi%2C%20Jiahui%20Yu%2C%20and%20Hongyu%20Ren.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHassabis%20said%20that%20while%20it%20is%20%26quot%3Brational%26quot%3B%20for%20Meta%20to%20be%20making%20these%20offers%2C%20many%20people%20in%20the%20AI%20space%20prioritize%20the%20mission%20to%20%26quot%3Bsteward%20that%20technology%20safely.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20more%20important%20things%20than%20just%20money%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BOf%20course%2C%20one%20has%20to%20pay%20people%20their%20market%20rates%20and%20all%20of%20these%20things%2C%20and%20that%20continues%20to%20go%20up.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeta%20did%20not%20reply%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider%20about%20Hassabis'%20comments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%20Anthropic's%20cofounder%20Benjamin%20Mann%20said%20that%20his%20researchers%20did%20not%20make%20a%20%26quot%3Bhard%20choice%26quot%3B%20to%20stay.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe've%20been%20maybe%20much%20less%20affected%20than%20many%20of%20the%20other%20companies%20in%20the%20space%20because%20people%20here%20are%20so%20mission-oriented%2C%26quot%3B%20Mann%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey%20get%20these%20offers%20and%20then%20they%20say%2C%20'Well%2C%20of%20course%20I'm%20not%20going%20to%20leave%20because%20my%20best%20case%20scenario%20at%20Meta%20is%20that%20we%20make%20money%2C%20and%20my%20best%20case%20at%20Anthropic%20is%20we%20affect%20the%20future%20of%20humanity.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22eb0bf243-8fb3-4e5a-b266-75192b14f213%5C%22%3E'We%20are%20doing%20well%20through%20this%20moment'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20month%2C%20Business%20Insider%20reported%2C%20based%20on%20federal%20visa%20filings%2C%20how%20much%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmuratis-new-ai-startup-salary-technical-talent-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etop%20AI%20labs%20are%20paying%20their%20technical%20staff%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOpenAI%20is%20paying%20an%20average%20of%20%24292%2C115%20to%20the%2029%20technical%20staffers%20listed%20in%20the%20filings%2C%20with%20the%20highest-paid%20position%20earning%20%24530%2C000%20and%20the%20lowest%20earning%20%24200%2C000.%20Anthropic%20pays%20an%20average%20of%20%24387%2C500%20to%2014%20technical%20hires%2C%20with%20the%20highest-paid%20position%20earning%20%24690%2C000%20and%20the%20lowest%20receiving%20%24300%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMira%20Murati's%20new%20AI%20startup%2C%20Thinking%20Machines%20Lab%2C%20is%20paying%20two%20members%20of%20its%20technical%20staff%20%24450%2C000%20in%20salary%2C%20while%20another%20is%20getting%20%24500%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHassab