laims%20it%20can%20help%20women%20navigate%20dating%20more%20safely%20and%20weed%20out%20the%20worst%20guys.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftea-app-women-share-anonymous-dating-reviews-goes-viral-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETea%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20an%20app%20exclusively%20for%20women%2C%20lets%20them%20reverse%20image%20search%20men's%20photos%2C%20run%20background%20checks%20on%20potential%20suitors%2C%20and%20post%20reviews%20of%20men%2C%20either%20deeming%20them%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnev-schulman-kamie-crawford-catfish-red-green-flags-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egreen-flag%20or%20red-flag%3C%2Fa%3E%20daters.%20The%20company%20website%20says%20that%20%26quot%3BTea%20ensures%20that%20women%20have%20the%20information%20they%20need%20before%20meeting%20someone%20new%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20was%20born%20in%202023%20out%20of%20the%20desire%20of%20founder%20Sean%20Cook%2C%20a%20former%20product%20manager%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsalesforce-marc-benioff-ai-half-work-layoffs-employees-question-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESalesforce%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20to%20protect%20women%20like%20his%20mother%2C%20who%20the%20site%20says%20ran%20into%20catfishes%20and%20men%20with%20criminal%20records%20while%20online%20dating.%20Its%20site%20boasts%20that%20more%20than%201.6%20million%20women%20are%20on%20the%20app.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETea%20is%20the%20commodification%20of%20a%20whisper%20network%20%E2%80%94%20and%20a%20digital%20one%20that%20defeats%20the%20purpose%20of%20indirect%2C%20off-the-record%20communication%20by%20encouraging%20women%20to%20leave%20a%20written%20trail%20of%20allegations.%20That%20spreads%20the%20grievances%20to%20a%20large%20network%20of%20people%20with%20whom%20they%20haven't%20established%20rapport.%20And%20it's%20not%20the%20only%20one%20of%20its%20kind%3A%20there's%20also%20RAW%2C%20a%20dating%20app%20that%20lets%20women%20match%20with%20men%20and%20then%20give%20them%20green%2C%20beige%2C%20or%20red-flag%20ratings%2C%20which%20contribute%20to%20the%20rating%20on%20a%20respect%20meter%20that%20displays%20on%20their%20profiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20apps%20are%20the%20startup%20cousins%20of%20%26quot%3BAre%20We%20Dating%20the%20Same%20Guy%3F%26quot%3B%20Facebook%20groups%2C%20which%20became%20hotbeds%20of%20gossip%20on%20guys%20and%20encouraged%20women%20to%20share%20photos%2C%20names%2C%20and%20red%20flags%20of%20men%20they%20had%20dated%20or%20matched%20with%20on%20dating%20apps.%20Women%20have%20also%20harnessed%20the%20power%20of%20the%20TikTok%20algorithm%20to%20call%20out%20allegedly%20bad%20guys%20and%20potential%20cheaters%20%E2%80%94%20last%20week's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fastronomer-ceo-andy-byron-awkward-moment-coldplay-concert-viral-tiktok-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EColdplaygate%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20only%20the%20latest%20evidence%20of%20how%20easily%20someone%20can%20get%20spotted%20misbehaving%20and%20how%20quickly%20someone's%20once-private%20behavior%20can%20become%20meme%20fodder%20for%20the%20globe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20naming%20and%20shaming%20is%20a%20trend%20empowered%20in%20part%20by%20the%20ethos%20of%20the%20%23MeToo%20movement%2C%20but%20it%20is%20morphing%20into%20a%20dystopian%20%26quot%3BJohn%20Tucker%20Must%20Die%26quot%3B%20sequel.%20The%20men%20put%20on%20blast%20in%20these%20groups%20don't%20all%20rise%20to%20the%20level%20of%20sexual%20abusers%2C%20cheaters%2C%20thieves%2C%20and%20fake%20profiles%20%E2%80%94%20I've%20been%20lurking%20in%20dating%20Facebook%20groups%20for%20years%20and%20have%20also%20seen%20many%20women%20post%20photos%20of%20and%20accuse%20men%20of%20offenses%20like%20messaging%20too%20many%20women%20and%20ghosting.%20Some%20post%20about%20men%20they%20match%20with%20before%20even%20meeting%20them%2C%20seeking%20intel%20from%20any%20women%20who%20may%20know%20them.%20Even%20West%20Elm%20Caleb%20%E2%80%94%20who%20went%20viral%20in%202022%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftiktoks-message-to-managers-dont-be-nice-in-performance-reviews-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ETikTok's%20algorithm%3C%2Fa%3E%20propelled%20stories%20of%20women%20complaining%20about%20dating%20him%20to%20millions%20of%20FYPs%20%E2%80%94%20was%20described%20as%20nothing%20more%20nefarious%20than%20a%20serial%20love%20bomber%20and%20boundary%20crosser.%20Moving%20whisper%20networks%20into%20digital%20spaces%20raises%20questions%20about%20what%20qualifies%20as%20a%20red%20flag%3B%20does%20a%20person%20have%20to%20be%20abusive%2C%20or%20were%20they%20just%20a%20prolific%20swiper%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Facebook%20groups%20and%20TikTok%20posts%20were%20part%20of%20a%20grassroots%20movement.%20Tea%20is%20trying%20to%20own%20the%20moment%20by%20bringing%20the%20posts%20under%20its%20own%20umbrella.%20%26quot%3BUltimately%2C%20this%20app%20is%20another%20facet%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsilicon-valley-salary-divide-meta-microsoft-layoffs-100-million-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESilicon%20Valley's%3C%2Fa%3E%20wrongheaded%20idea%20that%20all%20we%20need%20is%20a%20tech%20fix%20for%20a%20societal%20crisis%20like%20gender-based%20violence%2C%26quot%3B%20Lia%20Holland%2C%20campaigns%20and%20communications%20director%20of%20the%20digital%20rights%20advocacy%20group%20Fight%20for%20the%20Future%2C%20tells%20me%20in%20an%20email.%20If%20people%20really%20wanted%20to%20protect%20women%2C%20Holland%20says%2C%20%26quot%3Bthese%20advocates%20would%20also%20be%20calling%20to%20dismantle%20the%20digital%20surveillance%20state%20that%20powers%20Tea%2C%20and%20for%20new%2C%20digital-age%20laws%20that%20re-establish%20the%20basic%20human%20right%20to%20privacy%20for%20all%20abuse%20survivors%2C%20all%20activists%2C%20and%20all%20people.%26quot%3B%20Tea%20declined%20to%20comment%20for%20this%20story.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhisper%20networks%20have%20sustained%20because%20the%20traditional%20systems%2C%20like%20the%20criminal%20justice%20system%2C%20colleges%2C%20and%20HR%20departments%20sometimes%20fail%20to%20respond%20effectively%20to%20women's%20complaints.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthemarkup.org%2Finvestigations%2F2025%2F02%2F13%2Fdating-app-tinder-hinge-cover-up%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDating%20apps%20themselves%20have%20often%20failed%3C%2Fa%3E%20terribly%20at%20removing%20dangerous%20men%20from%20their%20pools.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20any%20kind%20of%20surprise%20that%20women%20would%20try%20to%20alert%20one%20another%20and%20try%20to%20protect%20one%20another%20in%20whatever%20ways%20they%20can%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Deborah%20Tuerkheimer%2C%20a%20professor%20in%20the%20Northwestern%20University%20Pritzker%20School%20of%20Law%20and%20author%20of%20the%20book%20%26quot%3BCredible%3A%20Why%20We%20Doubt%20Accusers%20and%20Protect%20Abusers.%26quot%3B%20Even%20if%20abusers%20aren't%20formally%20punished%2C%20whisper%20networks%20have%20the%20effect%20of%20preventing%20some%20women%20from%20engaging%20with%20men%20who%20could%20harm%20them.%20%26quot%3BThere%20are%20good%20things%20about%20informal%20reporting%20channels%2C%26quot%3B%20Tuerkheimer%20says.%20But%20stopping%20gender-base%20violence%20and%20harassment%20would%20require%20more%20accountability%20from%20our%20institutions.%20%26quot%3BIdeally%2C%20this%20would%20mostly%20be%20sort%20of%20a%20transition%20to%20a%20time%20when%20we%20all%20were%20more%20trusting%2C%20and%20had%20good%20reason%20to%20trust%20that%20these%20institutions%20would%20do%20what%20they're%20designed%20to%20do%2C%20because%20there's%20a%20lot%20that%20is%20lost%20when%20you%20have%20to%20go%20online%20or%20go%20to%20an%20app%20and%20make%20these%20allegations.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETea%20advertises%20itself%20as%20a%20place%20for%20%26quot%3Banonymous%20dating%20reviews%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20those%20who%20post%20to%20Tea%20aren't%20as%20anonymous%20as%20users%20may%20believe.%20The%20company's%20privacy%20policy%20states%20that%20it%20may%20share%20your%20information%20to%20respond%20to%20lawful%20requests%20and%20legal%20processes%2C%20and%20the%20app%20collects%20your%20birth%20date%2C%20photo%2C%20location%2C%20and%20photos%20of%20IDs.%20That%20could%20open%20women%20who%20think%20they're%20posting%20in%20good%20faith%20to%20defamation%20suits%20by%20disgruntled%20men%20whose%20reputations%20suffer%20by%20what%20has%20been%20posted%20about%20them%2C%20even%20if%20it's%20accurate.%20A%20man%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmashable.com%2Farticle%2Fare-we-dating-the-same-guy-facebook-group-lawsuit-dismissed%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esued%20Meta%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20women%20who%20posted%20negative%20stories%20about%20dating%20him%20in%20a%20Facebook%20group%20in%20Chicago%2C%20but%20a%20judge%20tossed%20the%20suit%20out%20in%20May.%20Another%20man%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.latimes.com%2Fcalifornia%2Fstory%2F2024-04-09%2Fdating-the-same-guy-defamation-lawsuit%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efiled%20a%20similar%20complaint%20in%20Los%20Angeles%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20prompting%20the%20women%20to%20start%20a%20GoFundMe%20to%20cover%20their%20legal%20fees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECook%2C%20Tea's%20founder%2C%20said%20on%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.podbean.com%2Fmedia%2Fshare%2Fpb-bsees-18a7708%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epodcast%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20May%20that%20the%20company%20receives%20an%20average%20of%20three%20legal%20threats%20a%20day%2C%20and%20has%20a%20legal%20team%20to%20respond.%20%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20whole%20men's%20rights%20activism%20community%20that%20doesn't%20like%20what%20we're%20doing.%20And%20so%20they're%20constantly%20trying%20to%20tear%20us%20down%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20that%20are%20unhappy%20about%20what%20we're%20doing%2C%20and%20that's%20OK%20with%20us.%20We%20believe%20this%20is%20a%20public%20service.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe're%20accustomed%20to%20having%20access%20to%20information%20to%20quell%20our%20anxieties.%20Little%20is%20more%20anxiety-inducing%20than%20getting%20ready%20for%20a%20first%20date.%20Some%20women%20have%20tried%20to%20beat%20that%20by%20playing%20amateur%20private%20investigator%20and%20digging%20deep%20on%20men%20before%20meeting%20up%20for%20a%20drink.%20It's%20partly%20driven%20by%20wanting%20to%20feel%20secure%20in%20a%20world%20where%20women's%20safety%20is%20always%20precarious%2C%20partly%20by%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-dating-startups-and-apps-disrupting-the-industry-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edesire%20to%20optimize%20their%20dating%20lives%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20crowdsource%20intel%20so%20they%20don't%20waste%20a%20night%20on%20a%20red-flag%20guy.%20But%20using%20selfies%20to%20verify%20someone's%20gender%20%E2%80%94%20Tea's%20method%20to%20confirm%20users%20are%20women%20%E2%80%94%20doesn't%20vet%20the%20legitimacy%20of%20such%20complaints.%20%26quot%3BThe%20fact%20that%20anyone%20from%20a%20vindictive%20ex%20to%20some%20lady%20on%20Fiverr%20can%20use%20this%20app%20to%20create%20false%20data%20also%20deeply%20undermines%20its%20legitimacy%2C%26quot%3B%20Holland%20says.%20%26quot%3BTrue%20predators%20are%20smart%20%E2%80%94%20they%20could%20use%20the%20app%20to%20get%20good%20'reviews'%20and%20lure%20unsuspecting%20dates%20with%20a%20false%20sense%20of%20security.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPart%20of%20meeting%20new%20people%20is%20ultimately%20to%20assume%20some%20level%20of%20risk%2C%20and%20dating%20requires%20both%20vulnerability%20and%20patience%20to%20unravel%20the%20nuance%20of%20someone's%20personality.%20As%20the%20writer%20Magdalene%20Taylor%20wrote%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fmagdajtaylor%2Fstatus%2F1948167749689114973%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EX%3C%2Fa%3