r%20own%20restrictions%20as%20to%2C%20for%20example%2C%20we%20restrict%20our%20speeding%20limit%20to%2040%20miles%20per%20hour%20%E2%80%A6%20and%20if%20the%20vehicle%20wants%20go%20on%20like%20higher%20speed%20roads%2C%20we%20can%20stop%20the%20vehicle%2C%20but%20those%20are%20out%20of%20convenience%20as%20opposed%20to%20safety%20critical%20nature.%20So%20far%20this%20service%20has%20been%20really%20well%20received%2C%20and%20we%20continue%20to%20expand%20on%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fsection%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20short%2C%20a%20couple%20of%20vehicles%20drove%20about%207%2C000%20miles%20in%20Austin%20without%20alarming%20safety%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20lack%20of%20critical%20safety%20incidents%20is%20great%20news%20for%20investors%2C%20but%20otherwise%2C%20there%20were%20not%20many%20other%20details.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%20said%20on%20Wednesday's%20call%20he%20expects%20autonomous%20Teslas%20to%20be%20available%20to%20%26quot%3Bprobably%20half%20of%20the%20population%20of%20the%20US%20by%20the%20end%20of%20the%20year%2C%26quot%3B%20pending%20government%20approval.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20a%20lot%20of%20places%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ETesla%3C%2Fa%3E%20would%20need%20to%20cover%20and%20a%20lot%20of%20regulatory%20hoops%20to%20jump%20through%20in%20roughly%20five%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETesla%20recently%20expanded%20robotaxi's%20service%20area%20in%20Austin%2C%20just%20a%20few%20weeks%20after%20it%20debuted%20to%20a%20limited%20number%20of%20invitees.%20On%20X%2C%20the%20company%20and%20Musk%20proudly%20showed%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-new-robotaxi-geofence-austin-shape-elon-musk-bigger-waymo-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ephallic-shaped%20geofence%20expansion%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20essentially%20said%20to%20competitors%2C%20%26quot%3BMine%20is%20bigger%20than%20yours.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20that%20move%2C%20Tesla%20made%20no%20mention%20of%20how%20many%20robotaxis%20it%20would%20add%20to%20the%20roads%20or%20whether%20it%20would%20invite%20more%20people%20to%20meet%20the%20potential%20increased%20demands%20of%20a%20larger%20service%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20far%2C%20we%20only%20know%20the%20figures%20Musk%20gave%20during%20April's%20earnings%20call%2C%20when%20the%20CEO%20said%20Tesla%20would%20start%20with%2010%20to%2020%20Model%20Ys.%20The%20service%20is%20still%20limited%20to%20invite-only.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETesla%20and%20a%20few%20folks%20on%20the%20company's%20Autopilot%20team%20didn't%20respond%20to%20questions%20posed%20on%20X%20about%20the%20vehicle%20numbers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20spokesperson%20for%20Tesla%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2264c9bbba-5fbc-4a97-9e84-74bf149caa7c%5C%22%3EWhat%20analysts%20want%20from%20Tesla%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAnalysts%20told%20BI%20they%20would%20like%20to%20see%20a%20few%20robotaxi%20data%20points.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERight%20now%2C%20a%20safety%20monitor%20sits%20on%20the%20front%20passenger%20side%20of%20every%20robotaxi.%20Data%20around%20human%20intervention%20or%20miles%20driven%20per%20disengagement%20is%20crucial%20because%20it%20can%20give%20investors%20some%20insight%20into%20when%20Tesla%20may%20feel%20confident%20enough%20to%20remove%20the%20human%20safety%20monitor%2C%20Munster%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-robotaxi-experience-human-intervention-incidents-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eone%20of%20my%20rides%20in%20Austin%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20safety%20monitor%20had%20to%20stop%20the%20ride%20as%20the%20vehicle%20started%20to%20head%20toward%20the%20wrong%20direction%20on%20a%20one-way%20road.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20big%20picture%20is%20this%3A%20They're%20not%20comfortable%20at%20removing%20the%20observer%20right%20now%20because%20they%20know%20the%20smallest