r%20cleaner%20mining%20operations%20at%20the%20district%20level.%20While%20these%20efforts%20are%20commendable%2C%20they%20are%20still%20limited%20to%20a%20few%20states.%20Thus%2C%20it%20is%20crucial%20to%20anchor%20state%20just%20transition%20plans%20in%20state%20energy%20policies%20and%20mandate%20the%20submission%20of%20%E2%80%98just%20transition%20roadmaps%E2%80%99%20to%20ensure%20binding%20commitments%20and%20alignment%20with%20central%20energy%20goals.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E2.%20Early%20reskilling%20and%20workforce%20planning%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20district-level%20workforce%20mapping%20in%20coal%20regions%2C%20including%20formal%2C%20informal%2C%20and%20dependent%20populations%2C%20should%20be%20conducted%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20workforce%20in%20the%20coal%20sector%20is%20not%20affected%20by%20the%20transition.%20The%20targeted%20reskilling%20for%20jobs%20in%20solar%2C%20electric%20vehicles%20(EVs)%2C%20energy%20efficiency%2C%20and%20green%20hydrogen%20should%20be%20initiated%20at%20least%202%E2%80%933%20years%20before%20the%20projected%20mine%20or%20plant%20decommissioning%2C%20using%20the%20Skill%20Council%20for%20Green%20Jobs%20(SCGJ)%E2%80%93aligned%20curriculum.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-1_11zon-1753409739.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Reskilling%20coal%20sector%20workers%20for%20solar%2C%20EVs%2C%20and%20green%20hydrogen%20is%20key%20to%20a%20just%20transition.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-1_11zon-1753409739.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-1_11zon-1753409739-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-1_11zon-1753409739-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-1_11zon-1753409739-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-1_11zon-1753409739-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-475896%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EReskilling%20coal%20sector%20workers%20for%20solar%2C%20EVs%2C%20and%20green%20hydrogen%20is%20key%20to%20a%20just%20transition.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20not%20all%20coal-belt%20regions%20will%20offer%20the%20required%20green%20jobs%20to%20replace%20the%20coal%20workforce.%20Therefore%2C%20policies%20must%20support%20alternative%20livelihood%20options%20that%20are%20rooted%20in%20local%20contexts.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20should%20also%20target%20deployment%20of%20future%20projects%20under%20the%20Pradhan%20Mantri%20Kisan%20Urja%20Suraksha%20evam%20Utthan%20Mahabhiyan%20(PM-KUSUM)%2C%20as%20well%20as%20scale%20up%20agri-photovoltaics%20in%20the%20fossil-fuel-intensive%20districts%20of%20Jharkhand%2C%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20and%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%20This%20can%20help%20in%20creating%20new%20livelihood%20avenues%20for%20both%20skilled%20and%20semi-skilled%20rural%20youth.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20the%20solarisation%20initiative%20in%20the%20agriculture%20sector%20should%20be%20linked%20to%20skilling%20and%20local%20manufacturing.%20As%20per%20a%202023%20study%2C%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20solarisation%20initiative%20could%20generate%20over%201%20million%20jobs%20in%20installation%2C%20sales%2C%20and%20maintenance%20across%20rural%20India.%20The%20government%20should%20create%20district-level%20skilling%20programmes%20linked%20to%20solar%20installation%2C%20pump%20repair%2C%20and%20energy%20entrepreneurship.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUltimately%2C%20reskilling%20is%20insufficient%20if%20jobs%20remain%20informal%2C%20precarious%2C%20or%20unsafe.%20Policies%20must%20mandate%20job%20quality%20standards%20that%20focus%20on%20aspects%20such%20as%20social%20security%20and%20occupational%20safety.%20These%20safeguards%20should%20be%20embedded%20into%20agreements%20negotiated%20at%20the%20time%20of%20plant%2Fmine%20closure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E3.%20Enact%20legal%20safeguards%20for%20fossil%20fuel%20workers%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20India%20has%20more%20than%202%20million%20workers%20directly%20or%20indirectly%20employed%20in%20the%20coal%20sector%2C%20it%20lacks%20statutory%20safeguards%20for%20workers%20who%20are%20displaced%20from%20employment%20due%20to%20the%20energy%20transition.%20There%20is%20a%20need%20to%20introduce%20an%20act%20to%20ensure%20pension%20portability%20and%20provide%20retraining%20grants%2C%20wage%20insurance%2C%20and%20priority%20in%20green%20job%20placement%20programmes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-2_11zon-1-1753409850.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Over%202%20million%20workers%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20coal%20sector%20need%20legal%20safeguards%20and%20retraining%20support.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-2_11zon-1-1753409850.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-2_11zon-1-1753409850-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-2_11zon-1-1753409850-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-2_11zon-1-1753409850-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-2_11zon-1-1753409850-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-475898%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EOver%202%20million%20workers%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20coal%20sector%20need%20legal%20safeguards%20and%20retraining%20support.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20in%20Canada%2C%20the%20Sustainable%20Jobs%20Act%20(formerly%20the%20Just%20Transition%20Act)%20mandates%20the%20creation%20of%20a%20Sustainable%20Jobs%20Partnership%20Council%2C%20which%20comprises%20representatives%20from%20labour%2C%20industry%2C%20and%20environmental%20sectors.%20It%20prioritises%20training%2C%20income%20support%2C%20and%20early%20planning%20for%20fossil%20fuel%20workers%2C%20ensuring%20that%20labour%20unions%20have%20a%20seat%20at%20the%20table.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20South%20Africa%E2%80%99s%20Just%20Energy%20Transition%20Investment%20Plan%20(JET-IP)%20recognises%20coal%20miners%20and%20energy%20workers%20as%20central%20stakeholders.%20The%20government%20has%20committed%20to%20establishing%20labour%20transition%20plans%20alongside%20infrastructure%20decommissioning%20as%20legal%20and%20institutional%20safeguards%20for%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E4.%20Localise%20RE%20manufacturing%20hubs%20in%20coal-dependent%20regions%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETransition%20policies%20should%20place%20an%20additional%20focus%20on%20coal-dependent%20regions%2C%20such%20as%20Jharkhand%2C%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20and%20Odisha.%20These%20areas%20face%20triple%20risks%20of%20job%20losses%2C%20state%20revenue%20shortfalls%2C%20and%20stalled%20economic%20activity.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-3_11zon-1753410040.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20a