utral.%20However%2C%20studies%20show%20that%20women%20hold%20less%20than%2011%25%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20RE%20jobs.%20Skilling%20programmes%20under%20Skill%20India%20and%20National%20Skill%20Development%20Corporation%20(NSDC)%20should%20include%20gender%20quotas%20and%20training%20in%20distributed%20RE%2C%20EV%20maintenance%2C%20and%20green%20construction%2C%20targeting%20rural%20women%2C%20marginalised%20workers%2C%20and%20informal%20sector%20labourers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E6.%20Ensure%20fair%20and%20inclusive%20land%20use%20for%20the%20energy%20transition%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELand%20plays%20a%20crucial%20role%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20clean%20energy%20transition%2C%20yet%20it%20often%20receives%20little%20attention%20in%20policy%20discussions.%20Large-scale%20RE%20projects%20and%20the%20closure%20of%20coal%20mines%20both%20require%20significant%20land%20use%20changes%2C%20which%20can%20lead%20to%20displacement%2C%20loss%20of%20livelihoods%2C%20and%20conflict%2C%20especially%20in%20tribal%20and%20forest%20areas.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-4_11zon-1753410144.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Repurposing%20degraded%20coal%20mine%20land%20for%20solar%20parks%20can%20align%20energy%20and%20local%20development%20needs.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-4_11zon-1753410144.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-4_11zon-1753410144-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-4_11zon-1753410144-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-4_11zon-1753410144-768x402.jpg%207