20more%20responsible%2040-something.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225760%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Steering%20wheel%20in%20BYD's%20Sealion%207.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F688070f4f748d8c055f61aa2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223840%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20car%20drives%20well%20on%20winding%20roads.%3Cp%3EAzfar%20Hashim%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20worth%20highlighting%20how%20refined%20the%20Sealion%207%20feels%20in%20everyday%20driving.%20On%20the%20expressway%2C%20it%20cruises%20comfortably%20at%20fast%20speeds%20with%20minimal%20wind%20or%20road%20noise.%20Tire%20noise%20is%20slightly%20noticeable%2C%20though%20%E2%80%94%20this%20variant%20runs%20on%20performance-oriented%20Michelin%20Pilot%20Sport%20EVs%2C%20which%20tend%20to%20be%20louder%20due%20to%20their%20tread%20pattern.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20that%20hardly%20matters%20when%20you%20have%20the%20standard%2012-speaker%20DynAudio%20sound%20system%20and%20double-glazed%20windows.%20Together%2C%20they%20ensured%20I%20could%20enjoy%20my%20playlist%20without%20interruption.%20For%20the%20curious%3A%20Bruno%20Mars%2C%20The%20Weeknd%2C%20Sam%20Smith%2C%20John%20Mayer%2C%20Stereophonics%2C%20and%20Fuel%20were%20part%20of%20the%20mix.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%2015.6-inch%20touchscreen%20rotates%20to%20portrait%20mode%20and%20controls%20everything%20from%20windows%20and%20climate%20to%20in-car%20karaoke.%20When%20karaoke%20is%20activated%2C%20the%20screen%20displays%20a%20QR%20code%20that%20passengers%20can%20scan%20%E2%80%94%20so%20drivers%20don't%20get%20distracted%20by%20the%20lyrics.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22BYD%20Sealion%207%20touchscreen.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68808b4885e81483682e8164%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%2015.6%20touchscreen%20can%20rotate%20to%20portrait.%3Cp%3EAzfar%20Hashim%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBack%20in%202008%2C%20I%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchinese-electric-car-deepal-s07-test-drive-review-ev-suv-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ereviewed%20a%20Chinese%20SUV%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20a%20time%20when%20the%20country%20was%20still%20new%20to%20exporting%20cars.%20I%20remember%20thinking%20its%20handling%20was%20underwhelming%2C%20even%20questioning%20how%20safe%20it%20would%20be%20in%20an%20emergency%20maneuver.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWell%2C%20it's%20now%202025%2C%20and%20it's%20clear%20that%20ride%20and%20handling%20have%20improved.%20In%20this%20all-wheel-drive%20variant%2C%20I%20would%20be%20confident%20to%20take%20it%20down%20winding%20roads.%20Steering%20feedback%20is%20reassuring%2C%20and%20stopping%20power%20is%20just%20as%20strong.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EOn%20the%20inside%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225554%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Backseats%20in%20BYD's%20Sealion%207.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68807156f748d8c055f61aa5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223657%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20driver%20found%20that%20the%20back%20seats%20were%20too%20low.%3Cp%3EAzfar%20Hashim%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20seats%20are%20comfortable%20and%20well-cushioned%2C%20offering%20solid%20support%20for%20long%20drives.%20That%20said%2C%20I%20found%20the%20back%20seats%20were%20a%20bit%20low%20for%20my%20liking%20%E2%80%94%20a%20matter%20of%20personal%20preference%2C%20but%20worth%20keeping%20in%20mind%20for%20taller%20passengers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20driving%20position%20is%20excellent%2C%20with%20great%20outward%20and%20all-around%20visibility.%20All%20the%20key%20controls%20are%20within%20easy%20reach%2C%20and%20the%20steering%20wheel%20is%20perfectly%20sized%20for%20a%20confident%20grip.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20there's%20one%20area%20that%20could%20be%20improved%2C%20it's%20the%20font%20size%20on%20the%20driver%20display.%20It's%20slightly%20too%20small%2C%20especially%20for%20those%20not%20quite%20ready%20for%20reading%20glasses%2C%20but%20not%20far%20off%20either.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20found%20the%20Driver%20Attention%20Warning%20overly%20sensitive%20%E2%80%94%20it%20popped%20up%20every%20time%20I%20yawned%2C%20displaying%20a%20coffee%20icon%20and%20suggesting%20I%20take%20a%20break%2C%20which%20became%20mildly%20irritating.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225760%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22BYD%20Sealion%207%20with%20a%20grassy%20hill%20in%20the%20background.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68808961f748d8c055f61b00%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223840%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20driver%20was%20impressed%20with%20the%20car's%20handling.%3Cp%3EAzfar%20Hashim%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20returned%20the%20keys%20to%20the%20BYD%20Sealion%207%20feeling%20genuinely%20impressed.%20While%20I%20haven't%20tested%20the%20more%20affordable%20Premium%20variant%2C%20the%20extra%2042%2C620%20Chinese%20yuan%20for%20the%20AWD%20Performance%20model%20feels%20justified.%20It%20has%20stronger%20performance%2C%20larger%20wheels%20with%20better%20tires%2C%20and%20an%20all-wheel-drive%20system%20that%20adds%20both%20confidence%20and%20capability.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20drove%20223%20miles%20on%20a%20full%20charge%20and%20returned%20the%20car%20with%207%25%20battery%20remaining%20%E2%80%94%20about%2020%20miles%20of%20range.%20That%20falls%20slightly%20short%20of%20the%20brochure's%20quoted%20460%20km%2C%20or%20286%20miles%2C%20WLTP%20range%2C%20but%20in%20real-world%20conditions%2C%20it's%20still%20solid%20for%20everyday%20use.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbyd-sealion-7-chinese-suv-ev-test-drive-fast-acceleration-2025-7%5C%22%3EBusin