ustsainable-home-with-plastic-bottles-and-mud-chuzi-vinu-daniel%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMud%20construction%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20slower%2C%20seasonal%20process%20that%20calls%20for%20patience.%20It%20dries%20more%20slowly%20in%20winter%20compared%20to%20summer.%20Each%20layer%20needs%20time%20to%20dry%20and%20settle%20before%20the%20next%20is%20added.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20significant%20challenge%2C%20Aishwarya%20points%20out%2C%20is%20finding%20skilled%20artisans%20familiar%20with%20these%20techniques.%20%E2%80%9CHowever%2C%20local%20workers%20can%20be%20trained%20in%20natural%20building%20and%20plastering.%20It%20not%20only%20ensures%20quality%20execution%2C%20but%20also%20empowers%20the%20local%20workforce%2C%20creates%20jobs%2C%20and%20boosts%20the%20local%20economy%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20reasons.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E2.%20Terracotta%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20biophilic%20design%20is%20what%20the%20architects%20at%20Venkataramanan%20Associates%20were%20going%20for%20when%20they%20designed%20The%20Earth%20Centre%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20a%20project%20developed%20and%20envisioned%20by%20Vista%20Spaces%2C%20using%20terracotta%20as%20the%20hero%20material.%20As%20architect%20Dhiraj%20Chilakapaty%20explains%2C%20the%20building%E2%80%99s%20envelope%20comprises%20three%20tiers%20%E2%80%94%20a%20structural%20blockwork%20base%2C%20an%20insulating%20air%20cavity%2C%20and%20an%20extruded%20terracotta%20cladding.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20layered%20wall%20system%20significantly%20improves%20thermal%20performance%2C%20reducing%20heat%20ingress%20and%20thereby%20lowering%20the%20building%E2%80%99s%20cooling%20demand%20by%20150%20tonnes.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Vista%20Spaces%2C%20The%20Earth%20Centre%20reflects%20a%20forward-thinking%20approach%20to%20urban%20development%20%E2%80%94%20one%20that%20prioritises%20ecological%20performance%20and%20material%20sustainability%20in%20the%20heart%20of%20Bengaluru%E2%80%