.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-474376%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22936%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%20Vayal%E2%80%99s%20idea%20led%20to%20the%20creation%20of%20an%20affordable%2C%20easily%20replicable%20technique%20suited%20for%20village%20settings.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFunded%20by%20the%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fgroundwater.org%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20Groundwater%20Foundation%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20a%20few%20others%20from%20America%2C%20JalTara%20has%20impacted%20100%20villages%20in%20Mantha%2C%2050%20in%20Partur%2C%2020%20in%20Jalna%2C%20and%20two%20in%20Ghansangi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElaborating%20on%20its%20benefits%2C%20Vayal%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CFour%20months%20of%20rain%20seep%20into%20the%20ground%20through%20this%20pit%2C%20and%20the%20water%20level%20increases%20tremendously.%20The%20water%20that%20accumulates%20during%20heavy%20rains%20drains%20through%20the%20pit%2C%20and%20due%20to%20continuous%20water%20seeping%20for%20four%20months%2C%20moisture%20builds%20up%20in%20that%20one%20acre.%20From%20that%20moisture%2C%20microorganisms%20survive%20and%20produce%20micronutrients%2C%20which%20benefit%20crop%20yield.%20Interestingly%2C%20earlier%20disputes%20over%20flooded%20fields%20have%20significantly%20reduced.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20last%20three%20years%2C%20starting%20in%202022%2C%201%2C75%2C000%20soak%20pits%20have%20been%20laid%2C%20rejuvenating%20the%20water%20table%20and%20enabling%20farmers%20to%20sow%20timely%20Rabi%20crops%2C%20breaking%20the%20cycle%20of%20drought.%20As%20Vayal%20points%20out%2C%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201248px)%20100vw%2C%201248px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FA-ready-soak-pit_11zon-1753180238.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221248%5C%