3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEven%20with%20proper%20patents%20and%20publications%2C%20the%20industry%20would%20take%20at%20least%20three%20years%20to%20switch%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20in%20three%20years%2C%20a%20lot%20can%20happen%20at%20the%20grassroots%20level.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20realisation%20shifted%20her%20focus.%20If%20industries%20weren%E2%80%99t%20ready%20to%20move%2C%20she%20would%20start%20with%20the%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ETaking%20the%20method%20to%20the%20people%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESushmita%20knew%20the%20method%20would%20only%20matter%20if%20people%20could%20use%20it.%20So%20she%20began%20conducting%20hands-on%20workshops%2C%20sharing%20her%20process%20with%20students%2C%20educators%2C%20and%20women%20from%20local%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNow%20I%E2%80%99ve%20started%20training%20people%20to%20make%20paper%20from%20water%20hyacinth.%20Many%20colleges%20are%20interested%20in%20adapting%20it%20for%20their%20own%20use%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20National%20College%2C%20Trichy%2C%20she%20ran%20a%20two-day%20workshop%20that%20combined%20science%20with%20skill-building.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20had%20a%20theory%20session%20on%20the%20first%20day%20about%20water%20hyacinths%2C%20but%20the%20second%20day%20we%20had%20hands-on%20experience%20in%20creating%20the%20papers%20from%20scratch%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Ishika%2C%20a%20student%20who%20attended.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-media-text%5C%22%3E%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-media-text__media%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FSushmita-Krishnan-10_11zon-1753267842-500x664.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FSushmita-Krishnan-10_11zon-1753267842-500x664.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FSushmita-Krishnan-10_11zon-1753267842-226x300.jpeg%20226w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FSushmita-Krishnan-10_11zon-1753267842-768x1020.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FSushmita-Krishnan-10_11zon-1753267842-1156x1536.jpeg%201156w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FSushmita-Krishnan-10_11zon-1753267842-150x199.jpeg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FSushmita-Krishnan-10_11zon-1753267842-1200x1594.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FSushmita-Krishnan-10_11zon-1753267842.jpeg%201459w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-475034%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22664%5C%22%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-media-text__content%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20those%20students%20are%20using%20their%20own%20handmade%20paper%20for%20greeting%20cards%20and%20college%20events.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeyond%20campuses%2C%20she%20has%20also%20trained%20over%20150%20women%20%E2%80%94%20including%20a%20group%20of%20middle-aged%20women%20in%20Velachery%2C%20Chennai%2C%20supported%20by%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Environment.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20had%20two%20workshops%20for%20the%20Ministry%2C%20three%20for%20colleges%2C%20and%20a%20few%20more%20are%20lined%20up%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Sushmita%2C%20the%20goal%20was%20not%20just%20awareness%2C%20but%20adoption.%20The%20more%20people%20who%20learned%20the%20method%2C%20the%20more%20likely%20it%20was%20to%20catch%20on%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20in%20places%20overrun%20by%20hyacinth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20pond%20to%20page%3A%20The%20paper-making%20process%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20process%20of%20turning%20water%20hyacinth%20into%20paper%20is%20surprisingly%20simple%20%E2%80%94%20and%20designed%20to%20be%20both%20cost-effective%20and%20environmentally%20conscious.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20begins%20with%20harvesting%20the%20plant%E2%80%99s%20stems%2C%20which%20are%20then%20sun-dried%20and%20boiled%20in%20an%20alkaline%20solution%20to%20break%20down%20the%20fibres.%20This%20softened%20pulp%20is%20beaten%20and%20mixed%20with%20water%20and%20a%20natural%20plant-based%20binder%20to%20create%20a%20slurry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20mixture%20is%20poured%20onto%20mesh%20frames%2C%20where%20the%20water%20drains%20out%20and%20the%20thin%20layer%20of%20pulp%20is%20left%20to%20dry%20under%20the%20sun.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-media-text%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-media-text__content%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnlike%20many%20other%20small-scale%20paper%20makers%2C%20Sushmita%20does%20not%20rely%20on%20newspaper%20pulp%20to%20hold%20the%20paper%20together.%20Nor%20does%20she%20bleach%20it%20to%20make%20it%20look%20%E2%80%9Ccleaner%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20use%20only%20natural%20binders%2C%20and%20the%20paper%20retains%20its%20natural%20greenish%20tint.%20I%20believe%20the%20quality%20of%20paper%20is%20defined%20by%20how%20easy%20it%20is%20to%20write%20on%20%E2%80%94%20not%20just%20how%20white%20it%20looks%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20entire%20process%20is%20quick%20and%20low-cost.%20%E2%80%9CWith%201%20kg%20of%20wet%20water%20hyacinth%2C%20you%20can%20make%2030%20A4%20sheets%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20estimates.%20%E2%80%9CFrom%20harvesting%20to%20making%20the%20pulp%2C%20it%20takes%20about%2025%20minutes.%20The%20drying%20takes%20another%2045.%20With%20practice%2C%20you%20can%20do%20it%20even%20faster%20%E2%80%94%20maybe%20in%2015%20minutes.%20And%20the%20cost%20per%20sheet%20shouldn%E2%80%99t%20be%20more%20than%20Rs%202.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-media-text__media%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%2050